{"tid":1012954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊先生：華航唔應該搵旅客嚟咁搞，影響國家形象。","createTime":"2019-02-08T03:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T04:09:30.000Z","uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7731ed5b23a5d1803766ab963a254748db1a9565","tid":1012954,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:45:43.000Z","msg":"華航發生工潮，今明有多班往來台灣和香港的航班需要取消。美麗華旅遊今早出發的一個「高雄、台北5天團」亦受今次工潮影響，飛往高雄的航班取消，不過旅程未受太大影響。領隊楊先生表示，公司得知工潮後已作出應變，旅行團會改為先飛往台北，「由台北玩番落高雄」，最後由高雄回港，預計整個行程不會受太大影響，最多是「飛行時間多少少」。楊先生稱，全團旅客22人，萬一由高雄回港的航班屆時被取消，相信公司會安排到其他航班讓團友回港。<br />\n<br />\n參加「高雄、台北5天團」的團友魏先生稱，今早看新聞得知華航發生工潮，在前往機場途中，領隊已通知團友行程將改由「台北玩番落高雄」，認為「旅行社反應幾快」。對於回港時候的安排，楊先稱不太擔心，「應該有飛機返港」；對於華航機師的行動，楊先生認為：「<span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該搵旅客嚟咁搞，影響國家形象。</span>」"},{"pid":"6bfe7fee79d6316fa2d60afcd568e625d2b1b3f7","tid":1012954,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"台灣架"},{"pid":"0907627e61ae753350510c9f8402559337f78714","tid":1012954,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bfe7fee79d6316fa2d60afcd568e625d2b1b3f7","tid":1012954,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"台灣架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"台灣國"},{"pid":"8d1504b124ddfeee41e58e1585b224051f6a35a5","tid":1012954,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">楊先生醒！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3dbbb9bc6f0b506e1c20dcd3400a4e7c8fee611d","tid":1012954,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0907627e61ae753350510c9f8402559337f78714","tid":1012954,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bfe7fee79d6316fa2d60afcd568e625d2b1b3f7","tid":1012954,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:46:11.000Z","msg":"台灣架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:46:42.000Z","msg":"台灣國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:54:27.000Z","msg":"中國"},{"pid":"f6c9765f0f9ed0b6b541faea1189aed55fbc5d1c","tid":1012954,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"台狗咪影衰我地中國"},{"pid":"e633dcdbd05a51aac01aef00baf0bc602fdeaa7b","tid":1012954,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"五毛狗即時撲出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cc35fbfb01c7c1f6f4f4b4fef83f258f315b90","tid":1012954,"uid":66447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:05:33.000Z","msg":"工潮罷工都仲要顧住你感受 咁仲罷黎拓柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab3042594c658dff629ddf944f1fbfd2402afce8","tid":1012954,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多香港人心入面台灣不嬲都係一個獨立主權國家"}]}